{
  "stem": "1721.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We'll take you to another little camp, you won't see the kid for another two weeks.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I think that lot of Jewish mothers wouldn't have done it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They would have wanted to keep their kids close by, and close knit family, and all that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I believe a lot of-- Joan's mother, Joan, my wife, would not have done that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "If it had been her in the same situation, she'd have said no, you're not taking my kid.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So although it turned out to be a very positive experience, I think she-- it was not much of a decision for her to say, go.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So anyway, I went up there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a nice positive experience.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember the lake and the trees, and upstate New York.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't meet Eddie Cantor, but it was his camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But would you have known who he was if you did?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no idea.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had no idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But he sponsored it, and it was a very famous thing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we came back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when we came back my mother had already-- my mother and stepfather at that time had already found a-- an apartment down in the Lower East Side, Clinton Street and Houston Street, which was right in the heart of, of the Jewish-- I mean the Yiddish theater's there and the whole nine yards of what Jewish life really was.",
      "word_count": 60
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so that's where they settled in for a number of years and started their life in America.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I went to school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Went to a-- to a local grade school there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now I was 11 years old.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Never had any formal schooling.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, actually I didn't go unwillingly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was pretty flexible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so I went.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
